        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嘿……！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 125,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "有人从我背后伸出手来，试图拽住我的左臂。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 126,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "芬妮",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哈呃——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 127,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "本能先于思考而采取了行动——左脚向后撤开半步，抬高左手，侧过身体，让对方因扑空而向前踉跄……",
